{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a responsive vertical timeline section for a Shopify product page with scroll animations and full customization.
    
    Layout & Content:
    
    Section Title: 'What Should I Expect From Consistent Use of Primal Queen?' (editable text, font, size, and color).
    
    Vertical divider line in the center with milestone circles along the line.
    
    Milestones display on alternating left/right (desktop view).
    
    Example milestones (editable):
    
    1 Week → card with icon + text.
    
    1 Month → card with icon + text.
    
    2 Months → card with icon + text.
    
    3 Months → card with icon + text.
    
    Each milestone has:
    
    Icon (editable, with animation).
    
    Heading (editable).
    
    Description text (editable).
    
    Product images can be placed left/right of the timeline (editable).
    
    Animations & Interactions:
    
    Scroll Effect: Divider line gradually fills from pink → black as user scrolls.
    
    Circle Animation: Circles fill with color (pink → black) when their milestone is reached, with an arrow fill animation pointing to the milestone card.
    
    Card Animation: Each card slides in/out from its side (left/right on desktop, right only on mobile) when entering viewport.
    
    Icon Animation: Icons inside milestone cards rotate continuously (360° round animation).
    
    Customization Options:
    
    Fully customizable fonts, text sizes, and colors via Shopify editor.
    
    Divider line color, card background, circle style, shadow, and border-radius adjustable.
    
    Replace icons with any image/icon.
    
    Easily add/remove milestones dynamically.
    
    Product images editable/replacable.
    
    Responsiveness:
    
    Desktop → Vertical timeline with alternating left/right cards.
    
    Mobile → Timeline collapses into a single column, and all cards appear on the right side of the divider.
    
    Animations remain active and smooth on both desktop and mobile.
    
    Deliver a fully interactive, responsive, scroll-animated timeline section with customizable milestones, images, icons, fonts, and colors that replicates the exact design and layout of the provided screenshot.

{% enddoc %}
